{"tid":531750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【動畫】貨Van衝入旺角油站 撞爛5條油槍","createTime":"2018-01-17T07:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T08:00:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1e63e58d4769b3f7aec36ec328f836975a4aba4f","tid":531750,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:11:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180117/20277281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180117%2F20277281&d=vZqP73C4vtVS24xoHJ2BqW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d100bf7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180117%2F20277281&h=2f0f4000\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180117/20277281</a><br />\n<br />\n【動畫】貨Van衝入旺角油站<br />\n撞爛5條油槍<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一輛客貨車昨凌晨一時許沿塘尾道駛至近旺角道時，疑貪方便走捷徑，穿過油站直接駛出旺角道，其間失控撞向油站加油泵，一條加油喉管被扯斷，4支油槍被撞甩，客貨車倒後鏡飛甩，惟司機沒停車，加速撞毀油站閘口欄杆，高速轉出旺角道逃去。事件幸無引起火警，警方正追緝涉案客貨車及司機。<br />\n<br />\n當時有私家車正在加油，目睹經過的姓莊司機稱︰「見唔到架車有減速，直接駛過，我起初真係以為撞到油泵，好彩冇。」69歲姓丘油站職員見狀報警，他估計當時客貨車車速約70至80公里，警員到場調查及翻看閉路電視。<br />\n<br />\n油站位於旺角鬧市，故經常有車輛走捷徑穿過油站駛入旺角道，對油站引起不便，於一年前在旺角道出口加建欄杆。"},{"pid":"f50d813453d3b97652e6164a85b95100b7ff63ea","tid":531750,"uid":36551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:16:09.000Z","msg":"越黎越多人撞車後不顧而去，係黑警太撚廢定刑罰冇阻嚇力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2817717e66b0294cada6642ab9ab86d4c2ece5","tid":531750,"uid":73849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:19:12.000Z","msg":"而家度度都有cam仲走得甩嘅咩，盞衰多樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb30f15a83c63aeb8b9a80dfee4e56f4ee9639b","tid":531750,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:00:54.000Z","msg":"應該酒駕毒駕 唔係走黎都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}